seo: 帆软报表,信息泄露,FineReport2012,漏洞检测
summary: 该插件用于检测帆软报表 FineReport2012 的信息泄露漏洞，通过发送特定请求并分析响应内容来确认是否存在漏洞。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect information leakage vulnerabilities in FineReport2012. It sends specific requests and analyzes the response content to confirm whether there are any vulnerabilities.
